quran[20]{c,v,t}:
  26,20,"O maaki: \"Mi wa…óii …óum, ontuma hara min ko mi jeyaa…óo e majju…ìe …ìen"
  26,21,"Mi dogi on, tuma nde mi hulunoo on, Joomi am okkin mi Ganndal O wa…óin mi jeyaa…óo e Nulaa…ìe …ìen"
  26,22,"∆äum ko neema mo wajitirtaa mi …óum, fii a maccin…óinii …ìi…ó…ìe Israa'iila …ìen"
  26,23,"Fir'awna wi'i: \" Ko hommbo jeyi winndere nden"
  26,24,"O maaki: \"Ko Jooma kammuuli …óin e leydi ndin e ko woni kon hakkunde majji, si on laatike yananaa…ìe"
  26,25,"O wi'ani …ìen wonu…ìe ban≈ãe makko: \"Enee; on he…óataako"
  26,26,"O maaki: \"Joomi moo…óon e Jooma baabiraa…ìe ardii…ìe …ìen"
  26,27,"[Fir'awna] wi'i: \"Pellet, Nulaa…óo moo…óon on Nulaa…óo faade e moo…óon ko o feetu…óo"
  26,28,"O maaki: \"Ko Jooma funnaange e hirnaange e ko woni kon hakkunde majji, si on laatike hakkiloo…ìe"
  26,29,"[Fir'awna] wi'i: \"Mi woondii si jogitike rewetee…óo tanaa am, mi wa…óete jeyaa…óo dummbaa…ìe …ìen"
  26,30,"O maaki: \"Enee, hay si mi addanii ma huunde …ìanngunde"
  26,31,"[Fir'awna] wi'i: \"Awa addu …óum, si tawii ko e goongu …ìen jeyaa…óaa"
  26,32,"O werliiii tuggordu makko ndun, jaka ko ndu biidaande(ngoolwa) …ìannguba"
  26,33,"O yaltini junngo makko ngon, jaka yoo ko ngo rawnungo wonannde ndaaroo…ìe …ìen"
  26,34,"[Fir'awna] wi'ani mbatu ngun fee makko: \"Pellet, oo…óoo ko mbileejo heewu…óo ganndal"
  26,35,Himo faandii yaltinirgol on ka leydi moo…óon mbilewu makko ngun. Ko hun…óun yamir…óon
  26,36,"∆Åe wi'i : \"Nennu mo e musi…ó…óo makko on, nulaa e ca'e …óen moo…ìoo…ìe (mbile)"
  26,37,∆Åe addane kala mbileejo anndu…óo
  26,38,Mbilee…ìe …ìen moo…ìaa fii fodoore √±alaande anndaande
  26,39,"Yim…ìe …ìen wi'anaa: \"Taw si onon ko on moo…ìike(ndenndi)"
